# 🏥 Hospital Management System (Frontend Only)

A simple and responsive Hospital Management System built using *HTML, CSS, and JavaScript*. This project is entirely frontend-based and uses localStorage to store and manage data like patients, doctors, and appointments.

---

## 📌 Features

- ✅ Add & Delete Patients
- ✅ Add Doctors
- ✅ Schedule Appointments
- ✅ Search & Filter Patients, Doctors, and Appointments
- ✅ Responsive Design (Mobile & Desktop)
- ✅ Data persistence using localStorage
- ✅ Clean Light Mode UI

---

## 📁 Pages Overview

| Page              | Description                          |
|-------------------|--------------------------------------|
| index.html      | Dashboard & Navigation               |
| patients.html   | Add, View, Delete Patients           |
| doctors.html    | Add, View, Delete Doctors            |
| appointments.html | Schedule & View Appointments       |

---

## 💡 Tech Stack

- *HTML5*
- *CSS3*
- *JavaScript (ES6)*
- *localStorage* for client-side data

---